  "notes": "Sprint 106 - Anti-Vibecoding Quality Assurance System (SPEC-0001). Backend complete (2 API routes, vibecoding service, governance model, 95% coverage). Frontend complete (4 components: VibecodingDashboard, SignalBreakdown, RoutingDecisionCard, KillSwitchDashboard, plus useVibecodingIndex hook). Core feature calculates Vibecoding Index (0-100 risk score) from 5 weighted signals (Intent, Ownership, Context, Attestation, Rejection). Progressive routing: GREEN (0-30) auto-approve, YELLOW (31-60) tech lead, ORANGE (61-80) CEO optional, RED (81-100) CEO mandatory. Kill switch activates on rejection >80%, latency >500ms, or 5+ CVEs."
